            <article class="about_kz_pg"> 
            <p> Kazakhstan is a country with a huge territory, extensive tourist potential and incredible flavor. Many tourists are just beginning to discover this country, but its popularity and attractiveness for travelers is growing every year, and exponentially.
            </p>
            <p>It is definitely worth visiting the glorious city of Almaty, which many call a garden. It is located at the foot of the slopes of the Tien Shan and is notable for its natural beauty and a large number of interesting places to visit and spend leisure time. There are many parks, fountains, cathedrals, temples, museums and other attractions, and the mountain panorama, with an abundance of greenery and lakes, fascinates and inspires.</p>
            <p>After Almaty, you should visit the capital of Kazakhstan Astana, is a truly beautiful city that is developing rapidly. On its territory, modern architecture is extremely advantageously combined with the historical heritage, which is inherent in the oriental style. There will be a lot of impressions from visiting Astana, because this city of the future impresses with its sophistication and splendor.</p>
